Welcome to Haleness - your personal medical information tracker!


Haleness means to be in a state of robust good health; which can be 
achieved when you stay on top of your medical appointments, medication, 
and history.


The goal of this program is to let users: 
- keep track of their medical history
- immunization shots given and needed in the future 
- bills that are due
- appointments in the future 
- a calendar
- list of prescriptions
- timer to take medications 
- list of your doctors
- which hospitals you've attended